   "source": [
    "# Arithmetic Mean/Geometric Mean Inequality\n",
    "\n",
    "For non-negative [real numbers](real-numbers.ipynb) $a_1, a_2, \\ldots, a_n$, the inequality states that:\n",
    "$$ \\frac{a_1 + a_2 + \\cdots + a_n}{n} \\geq \\sqrt[n]{a_1 a_2 \\cdots a_n} $$"
   ]
  }
 ],
